headline: Silver Is Trading Like a Meme Stock
summary: A dizzying year-end rally has pushed silver prices about 160% higher in 2025, their largest annual climb since the inflationary shock of 1979. The metal's roughly 10% increase Tuesday marked a rebound from Monday, when futures slid almost 8.
